title: Nonfinancial Noncorporate Business; Unidentified Miscellaneous Liabilities (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
This series has been discontinued and will no longer be updated. It was a duplicate of the following series, which will continue to be updated: https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/NNBUMBQ027S

The FRED series Miscellaneous Liabilities - Liabilities - Balance Sheet of Nonfarm Noncorporate Business is now known as Nonfinancial Noncorporate Business; Unidentified Miscellaneous Liabilities.

The source series id is FL113193003.Q.

This series appears in Table B.104. For further information see the assistance provided in the guide to the Financial Accounts at https://www.federalreserve.gov/apps/fof/.
